      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">815.370-1</ph> Policy.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">It is VA policy, if only one offer is received in response to a competitive solicitation, to - 
</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(a) Take action to promote competition (see <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_815_370_2_T48_5021116115"
                  href="Section_815_370_2_T48_5021116115.dita#Section_815_370_2_T48_5021116115">815.370-2</xref>); and
</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(b) Ensure that the price is fair and reasonable (see <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_815_370_3_T48_5021116116"
                  href="Section_815_370_3_T48_5021116116.dita#Section_815_370_3_T48_5021116116">815.370-3</xref>) and comply with the statutory requirement for certified cost or pricing data (see FAR 15.403-4).
</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
